messages.content:
你是 marketting-planning 项目的 attribute agent。
只围绕当前多轮营销规划链路归因：request_normalization、intent_recognition、field_clarification、session_merge、path_dispatch、planning_function、result_assembly、sse_generation、adapter_extraction。
优先定位最早造成 planning 输出不满足 reference contract 的阶段；如果 target_value_unit_probe、execution_stage_probe 或 planning_output_probe 已复现错误，必须以这些探针证据作为高优先级根因依据。
只能输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段；证据不足时用 evidence_strength=none/weak 和 root_cause_hypothesis 表达缺口。
最终只输出 AttributeResult JSON 所需字段：expectation_attributions、suspected_locations、root_cause_hypothesis、evidence、evidence_strength。

## 输出约束：attribute 归因分析输出
你的输出必须是合法 JSON，且严格符合以下 JSON Schema：
```json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "expectation_attributions": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {
        "$ref": "#/$defs/ExpectationAttribution"
      },
      "minItems": 1
    },
    "suspected_locations": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "root_cause_hypothesis": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    },
    "evidence": {
      "type": "array",
      "items": {}
    },
    "evidence_strength": {
      "type": "string",
      "minLength": 1
    }
  },
  "additionalProperties": false,
  "$defs": {
    "ExpectationAttribution": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "expectation_id": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "fulfillment_status": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "suspected_locations": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        },
        "root_cause_hypothesis": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1
        },
        "evidence": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {}
        }
      },
      "additionalProperties": false,
      "required": [
        "expectation_id",
        "fulfillment_status"
      ]
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "expectation_attributions",
    "root_cause_hypothesis"
  ]
}
```

### 强约束
- 最终回答必须只包含一个 JSON object；不要输出 Markdown，不要使用 ```json 代码块，不要在 JSON 外输出解释、前缀或后缀。
- 最终回答首字符必须是 `{`，末字符必须是 `}`。
- JSON 字符串内部如需引用用户原词，禁止直接写未转义英文双引号；请使用中文引号“”或转义为 `\"`。
- 必须包含 `required` 列表中的所有字段。
- 每个字段值必须匹配 schema 中的类型。
- 以下字段必须非空（空字符串/空数组/空对象/None 均视为不合规，会被阻断）：['expectation_attributions', 'root_cause_hypothesis']
- `additionalProperties: false`：禁止输出 schema 未定义的字段。
- 禁止把 schema 里的类型描述符（如 "string"）原样当作内容填进去——每个字段必须填入真实内容。

{
  "expectation_attributions": [
    {
      "expectation_id": "意图正确识别为营销规划",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {"stage": "intent_recognition", "module": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py"}
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别模型将营销规划请求错误分类为“其他意图”（intent 4001），未映射到营销规划意图，导致流程直接进入 non_agent 并结束，无法启动后续营销规划流程。",
      "evidence": [
        "execution_stage_probe 中 intent_recognition actual_stage=non_agent，expected_stage=intent",
        "extracted_output intent=4001，intent_name=“其他意图”",
        "judge_result 中 missing 项：missing_correct_intent，wrong 项：wrong_intent_code"
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "根据缺少字段进入澄清阶段",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "由于意图识别错误，系统未进入营销规划澄清流程，而是直接结束，因此未识别 NBEV 目标差距等缺失字段。",
      "evidence": [
        "output_summary.stage=non_agent，end_flag=1",
        "session_summary.missing_fields 为空",
        "field_clarification evidence 显示 required_fields 为空，无澄清动作"
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "不生成规划卡片且不提前结束",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别错误导致流程提前结束（end_flag=1），尽管未生成卡片，但 completed 被置为 true，违反了参数不完整时应保持会话开放的预期。",
      "evidence": [
        "event_summary.completed=true，final_event=done",
        "card_summary 为空但与 completed 状态矛盾",
        "planning_output_probe expected_cards_count=0 但流程错误终止"
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "SSE事件流反映正确的阶段转换",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别错误后，sse_generation 直接以 done 事件结束，未产生澄清提示事件，前端无法正确展示等待用户输入的状态。",
      "evidence": [
        "event_summary 无 clarification_prompt，final_event=done",
        "protocol_completed=true 而非 false"
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "不应退回到fallback或non-agent路径",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [
        {"stage": "intent_recognition", "module": "app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py"}
      ],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "意图识别输出 4001（其他意图）导致 path_dispatch 将流程路由到 non_agent，未能停留在营销规划预期路径上。",
      "evidence": [
        "output_summary.stage=non_agent",
        "fallback.used=false 但 stage 错误",
        "reference_contract expected_stage=intent 未满足"
      ]
    },
    {
      "expectation_id": "mp_contract:expected_stage",
      "fulfillment_status": "not_fulfilled",
      "suspected_locations": [],
      "root_cause_hypothesis": "实际阶段 non_agent 与 contract 要求的 intent 阶段不一致，根因在于 intent_recognition 阶段输出了错误的 stage 分类。",
      "evidence": [
        "contract expected_stage=intent，actual stage=non_agent",
        "execution_stage_probe: intent_recognition actual_stage=non_agent"
      ]
    }
  ],
  "suspected_locations": [
    {"stage": "intent_recognition", "source_file": "ext_repo:app/workflow/steps/intent_recognition.py"},
    {"stage": "intent_recognition", "source_file": "ext_repo:app/workflow/prompts/intent_prompt.py"},
    {"stage": "intent_recognition", "source_file": "ext_repo:app/schemas/intent.py"},
    {"stage": "path_dispatch", "note": "可能依赖错误的 intent 进行路由，但主因在 intent 输出"}
  ],
  "root_cause_hypothesis": "intent_recognition 阶段未能将用户输入“我们团队今年的NBEV目标还差不少，能帮我看看怎么通过增加理财师或者优化产品方案来补上吗？”正确识别为营销规划意图，而是归类为 4001（其他意图），导致 path_dispatch 将流程路由到 non_agent 阶段并立即结束会话。后续 field_clarification、planning_function、result_assembly 等环节均未按预期执行，所有 reference contract 和业务预期均被破坏。",
  "evidence": [
    "execution_stage_probe: intent_recognition actual_stage=non_agent, expected_stage=intent",
    "planning_output_probe: actual_stage=null, stage_match=false, evidence_gap=[actual_stage]",
    "extracted_output: intent=4001, stage=non_agent, end_flag=1, completed=true",
    "judge_result: all business expectations not_fulfilled, missing correct intent, wrong stage routing, premature session end"
  ],
  "evidence_strength": "strong"
}

